Money…I didn’t even want it.

Angel Saber:

I didn’t get much for christmas… My family is poor… sort of… All you people who got ps3s and stuff are all spoilt! But i’m happy enough.

I didn’t get a PS3, I didn’t want one. Anyway, Christmas is just for fun/joy and I’m happy that your satisfied with what you got. I don’t really want anything for Christmas anymore. Well, I hope you all get what you wanted, and have a fun day!
